---
title: Lemon Tortelloni Palermo with Shrimp with Pesto, Roasted Bell Pepper & Parmesan
description: Tender tortelloni are pretty much great in any form, but they’re *especially* great when packed with soft ricotta cheese. Add tender roasted bell pepper slices and a squeeze of bright, tangy lemon juice to the mix and you’ve got yourself a pasta night for the books. This divine dish is taken to the next level with a creamy, Parmesan- and pesto-spiked sauce and a sprinkle of scallion greens. Be still, our pasta-loving hearts...
